original_title: UFC Fight Night 115: Volkov vs. Struve
overview: UFC Fight Night 115: Volkov vs. Struve was a mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship held on September 2, 2017 at Rotterdam Ahoy in Rotterdam, Netherlands. A heavyweight bout between former Bellator Heavyweight Champion Alexander Volkov and Stefan Struve headlined the event.
title: UFC Fight Night 115: Volkov vs. Struve
